{"tid":482232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★低端人口-----深入探討IT人的社會地位！","createTime":"2017-11-28T03:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T13:14:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a9408eae67aed38cef9e3cb4480e873963a35c86","tid":482232,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"IT雖受到社會各階層的歡迎，但以IT為生的職業低層員工卻屬於「賤民」，地位在基層市民之下。雖然有些當紅的IT人，能夠擠身豪們，成為達官貴人的座上客，然而在世人的眼中，他們的人格仍然是低下的，因為IT是供人娛樂的「玩意兒」，IT人就是為人取樂的。<br />\n<br />\n看不起IT人並不僅僅是官員，市民也同樣視IT為最下賤的職業。普通人家如有人去做「IT」，都會被認為是有辱家人，是不肖子孫。凡做「IT」的人要被開除族籍，名字不能上族譜，死後不能葬入宗族墳地。因此，很多人從IT之後，隱姓埋名，幾十年不與家人來往，以免玷辱祖宗。"},{"pid":"c9ae34b381c7577bd811f97c82588b0b245a706d","tid":482232,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fb0703c24875bb6705d47ce47847b770d99d62","tid":482232,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-V6B6W7JFX10/VWsmBx5HymI/AAAAAAAAiro/ArJxRaIqC_U/s640/1433078060_0565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-V6B6W7JFX10%2FVWsmBx5HymI%2FAAAAAAAAiro%2FArJxRaIqC_U%2Fs640%2F1433078060_0565.jpg&h=08cb647f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fae4dcb5d5555b1cc8eeb3ac56b627784d3ee94a","tid":482232,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nxxxx_<br />\n樓主個名變左咁既?"},{"pid":"44f568ec60d6baed2a76b54f2372c1df72afefc4","tid":482232,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nxxxx_<br />\n樓主個名變左咁既?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g